<h2 id="the-basics">The Basics</h2>
<p>Particle ã§ appears in a lot of different contexts, and is an important particle to wrap your mind around. Its meaning shifts depending on how it's used, but, at its core, particle ã§ helps specify <em>where</em> or <em>how</em> an activity or an event takes place. In this page, we'll walk you through the ins and outs of particle ã§, always referring back to the underlying concept it represents: specification.</p>

